<detall><id label=""><![CDATA[74953]]></id><title label="Titol"><![CDATA[Anything goes to get a loan]]></title><excerpt label="Resum"><![CDATA[El Crèdit, a play by Jordi Galceran and directed by Sergi Belbel returns to Villarroel. It stars Jordi Bosch and Jordi Boixaderas.]]></excerpt><content label="Contingut"><![CDATA[<p>El Crèdit [The loan] returns to Sala Villarroel after the holidays. It is one of the best of this season&#8217;s plays and has an excellent cast, featuring Jordi Bosch and Jordi Boixaderas.</p>
<p>Written by Jordi Galceran and directed by Sergi Belbel, it explains the relationship between a bank manager and a client who needs a loan. At first, the bank manager refuses the loan, but everything can change when the client says that if he isn&#8217;t given the money, he will use extremely forceful measures to get it.</p>
